    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements. Validation evidence demonstrates model adequacy across the nominal CPB operating envelope (3–5 L/min, 3000–3600 RPM). RH < 1.0 at all five nominal validation points. Edge cases involving high-shear-stress regions near blade tips at maximum rotational speed and low-flow near-stall conditions are studied separately. The model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions within the nominal CPB operating range for this Class II device.",
